<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">

    <title>Cocos Creator | <%= projectName %></title>

    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,user-scalable=no,initial-scale=1, minimum-scale=1,maximum-scale=1"/>
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes"/>
    <meta name="full-screen" content="yes"/>
    <meta name="screen-orientation" content="portrait"/>
    <meta name="x5-fullscreen" content="true"/>
    <meta name="360-fullscreen" content="true"/>
    
    <meta name="renderer" content="webkit"/>
    <meta name="force-rendering" content="webkit"/>
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge,chrome=1"/>
    
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="style.css"/>
    <link rel="icon" href="favicon.ico"/>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div>
      <ol>
        <li>move cursor: WASD</li>
        <li>move camera: up, down, left, right</li>
        <li>ok, cancel: enter, '(left side of enter)</li>
        <li>space: toggle robot</li>
        <li>不要在開頭畫面按cancel, 程式會終止</li>
        <li>要設定了駕駛員, 才可以派出機體</li>
        <li>請先將畫面縮小到75%</li>
      </ol>
    </div>
    <h1 class="header"><%= projectName %></h1>
    <div id="GameDiv" style="width:<%= previewWidth %>px; height: <%= previewHeight %>px;">
        <canvas id="GameCanvas" width="<%= previewWidth %>" height="<%= previewHeight %>"></canvas>
    </div>
    <p class="footer">
      Created with <a href="https://www.cocos.com/products" title="Cocos Creator">Cocos Creator</a>
    </p>
    <%- include(cocosTemplate, {}) %>
  </body>
</html>
